data.title: YCCC Announces Spring 2020 Honors – York County Community College
data.text:
The following students were named to the President’s List at York County Community College for academic achievement demonstrated by earning a 4.0 GPA for full-time study during the spring 2020 semester: Brandon Bullard, Berwick; Hannah Fernald, Sanford; Kayla Fuller, South Berwick; Jolena Lampron, Lyman; Hanson Matheson, Wolfeboro – NH; Ally McLellan, Presque Isle; Katherine Nolette, East Waterboro; Nicole Paquette; Sanford, Corrie Sweeney, North Waterboro; Ashley Wyatt, Eliot; Stiles Zuschlag, Lebanon.

The following students were named to the Dean’s List at York County Community College for academic achievement demonstrated by earning a 3.5 GPA for full-time study during the spring 2020 semester: Jonah Averill, Scarborough;
